<span id="freeTextContainer8525559943691606302">Published in 1994, this book follows the reliable and very readable Francis formula - this time our hero is a young film director who faces danger from people trying to sabotage his film loosely based a local death in Newmarket 26 years earlier. Easily read in one day.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


