  <div class="friendReviews elementListBrown" >
    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1924800543" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1924800543" />
    <a title="Carolyn (in SC) C234D" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1916753-carolyn-in-sc-c234d"><img alt="Carolyn (in SC) C234D" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1924800543?book_show_action=true">Feb 25, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Carolyn (in SC) C234D" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Carolyn (in SC) C234D" href="/user/show/1916753-carolyn-in-sc-c234d">Carolyn (in SC) C234D</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1916753-carolyn-in-sc-c234d?shelf=mystery-thriller-not-a-cozy">mystery-thriller-not-a-cozy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1916753-carolyn-in-sc-c234d?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1916753-carolyn-in-sc-c234d?shelf=suspense">suspense</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1916753-carolyn-in-sc-c234d?shelf=set-in-the-uk">set-in-the-uk</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1916753-carolyn-in-sc-c234d?shelf=featuring-animals">featuring-animals</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1924800543" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9152442460059316714">I&apos;ve enjoyed many of Dick Francis&apos;s mysteries over the years, although I haven&apos;t yet included all of them in my Goodreads listings. They are usually interesting, quick reads; I do not tend to read them as analytically as some of the other reviewers seem to. All I wrote fourteen years ago was that this was a good mystery featuring Thomas Lyon, a film director who needs to figure out who is stabbing people now, and what happened 26 years ago when a young woman was found hanged.</span>
  <span id="freeText9152442460059316714" style="display:none">I've enjoyed many of Dick Francis's mysteries over the years, although I haven't yet included all of them in my Goodreads listings. They are usually interesting, quick reads; I do not tend to read them as analytically as some of the other reviewers seem to. All I wrote fourteen years ago was that this was a good mystery featuring Thomas Lyon, a film director who needs to figure out who is stabbing people now, and what happened 26 years ago when a young woman was found hanged.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9152442460059316714" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


